thread.title: Fatima softball wins district championship

author: News Tribune
title: Fatima softball wins district championship
text:
Share 
LINN, Mo. — Fatima defeated South Callaway 5-2 on Friday to win the Class 2 District 10 championship. Macy Berhorst was the winning pitcher, allowing two hits and striking out seven. 
Berhorst also had three hits of her own and drove in one. Raegan Huhn had two hits and an RBI, and Erin Eichholz had a hit and two RBI. 
Fatima (19-9) plays the winner of Blair Oaks and Eugene in sectionals. ﻿
